1 This act would require the department of administration to provide a list of certified
2 minority and women-owned business enterprises to each prospective contractor of a construction
3 project and would prohibit the issuance of a waiver from this requirement until the contractor
4 received assistance from the department.
5 This act would take effect upon passage.
